OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy at first today,
OL,6,Fbut some brighter spells will develop
OL,7,Fat times. A few spots of rain are
OL,8,Fpossible where the cloud thickens.
OL,9,FBreezy, but feeling pleasant in the
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers largely easing away
OL,13,Fto leave a dry night, but skies
OL,14,Fremaining cloudy. A mild night under
OL,15,Fthe blanket of cloud.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FCloudy at first, with a few
OL,18,Foutbreaks of rain in the morning.
OL,19,FHowever, this will clear and skies
OL,20,Fwill brighten a little in the
OL,21,Fafternoon with some warm sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
